================================================================================

This script is a provisional version. There are two things you should pay attention to yourself.
1. If you want to separate the action of setting the toolchain from the compilation, set the toolchain path yourself. ex:export PATH=~/gcc-linaro-7.5.0-2019.12-x86_64_arm-linux-gnueabi/bin:$PATH
2. When compiling busybox, select static compilation.
Settings ->
- [*] Build static binary (no shared libs)


[Usage] ./total.sh [option]
--apt               Install the necessary software 
--compile_busybox   compile busybox
--compile_kernel    compile kernel
--compile_qemu      compile qemu
--setup_toolchain   download and setup environment variables of toolchain
--pack              Package TbusOS.img
--debug             Debugging TbusOS
--run               Default Running TbusOS
--auto              Automatically compile, set, and run
--clean             clean busybox kernel qemu
--clean_busybox     clean busybox
--clean_kernel      clean kernel
--clean_qemu        clean qemu

================================================================================